ic","justification":"This validates whether the real LLM surfaces and places decision content correctly, which is model-output quality and can vary run to run (LLM-DEP). A stub summary would hide this failure. Rejection gate: rejected Workflow because behavior can be tested with one real summarization call from transcript input; it does not require validating multiple sequential agentic handoffs.","test_description":"Feed transcripts containing explicit decision statements to the real summarizer and assert those decisions are present in the output `decisions` section and absent from narrative-only placement.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.02,"Integration":0.06,"System":0.04,"Agentic":0.7,"Workflow":0.18}},{"behavior_id":6,"description":"When the audio file is longer than 60 minutes, the service splits it into segments and processes them sequentially, merging the results into a single coherent summary.","minimum_level":"Workflow","justification":"This behavior explicitly requires sequential segment processing plus merged final coherence, i.e., multiple agentic steps and handoffs (MULTI-STEP). Integration with mocks can validate splitting order but misses real coherence regressions across segment summaries (MOCK-HIDE, INTEGRATION-BRAKE d).","test_description":"Run a >60-minute real meeting recording through the full segmentation path, confirm sequential per-segment processing occurs, and evaluate merged output for cross-segment coherence and complete structured sections.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.01,"Integration":0.05,"System":0.1,"Agentic":0.18,"Workflow":0.66}},{"behavior_id":7,"description":"The full pipeline (upload audio, transcribe, summarize, deliver structured output) completes without manual intervention for a real meeting recording.","minimum_level":"Workflow","justification":"This is an end-to-end multi-stage pipeline with real audio, STT model, su